&lt;h3&gt;Sales Strategy&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the Manager, Premium Sales to develop and implement targeted sales strategies for Premium Seating, Concert Memberships, and Suite Rentals for concerts, family shows, and special events at Amerant Bank Arena and War Memorial Auditorium&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute sal

