&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with internal departments to shadow workflows, identify pain points, and scope automation opportunities that translate manual effort into measurable time savings.&lt;/li&gt;
