&lt;h2&gt;About the Florida Panthers Foundation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Florida Panthers Foundation serves as the team&#39;s main charitable beneficiary, focused on making a positive philanthropic impact on the South Florida community and beyond. Through partnerships, grants, and community programs, the Foundation supports four priority areas: youth hockey, health and education initiatives for children, veterans&#39; issues, and the endangered Florida panther. The Foundation raises money through various in-game and community initiatives including the 50/50 Raffle, jersey and memorabilia auctions, and other fan engagement opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
