&lt;p&gt;Two-time Stanley Cup Champions. A sold-out Amerant Bank Arena. A fanbase that has fallen in love with a hockey team in South Florida. The Florida Panthers have built something special — and we&#39;re looking for a transformational creative leader to build a content strategy to match.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a rare chance to step into one of the most exciting franchises in professional sports and own the entire content ecosystem — from the electricity of a playoff hype reel to the thumb-stopping digital moment that brings a new fan into the fold. The Head of Content will have the creative license, the organizational support, and the platform to build content that reflects the Panthers brand and helps shape where we&#39;re going.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Strategy &amp;amp; Alignment&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute a bold, comprehensive content strategy that reflects the ambition of this organization and puts the Florida Panthers brand at the intersection of sport, culture, and storytelling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with the Creative Director, VP of Game Presentation, and VP of Digital Marketing to ensure visual consistency, strategic alignment, and cross-functional execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a forward-looking content roadmap with fans at the center — one that anticipates where culture is heading and positions this franchise as a leader in premium content&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
